workout_groups.name: Muscular Endurance
workout_groups.description: Increase strength endurance by performing high-rep bodyweight exercises.

workouts.name: Push-Up Burnout Set
workouts.description: Perform as many push-ups as possible, resting only when necessary.

workouts.name: Wall Sit Hold
workouts.description: Hold a deep wall sit position for as long as possible.

workouts.name: Plank Challenge
workouts.description: Hold a plank for as long as possible with minimal rest.

workouts.name: Bodyweight Squat Marathon
workouts.description: Perform as many squats as possible, maintaining proper form.

workouts.name: Triceps Dip Burnout
workouts.description: Perform high-rep triceps dips using a chair or low surface.
